                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This would make norrath's economy even worse than it already is with the bazaar.
<br />

<br />
Those of us that would not EVER pay RL cash for a GAME item would be sitting in the bazaar..."Where did all the ornate go?"  
<br />

<br />
Hmm...it's all being sold for $10 dollars on Sonybay.  
<br />

<br />
"Oh theres one....only 1000000pp"  And then the pp gets sold for 10 bucks on Sonybay.  
<br />

<br />
This poll is just idiocy and money grubbing on their part.
<br />

<br />
I understand that it happens outside of Sony's control.  BUT since it is "illegal" many people do not do it.  Make it "legal" and a bunch of people who don't do it now would end up doing it.  Causing SEVERE in game inflation.
<br />

<br />
I do, however, think that the ability to sell your account isn't so bad other than the fact that this would become the way to "sell items".  Make an account...put the item on it....sell the account.  
<br />

<br />
Basically, in the end, there is NO good way to allow this to happen.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
